title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2012 Mar 14 WE [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 14 March 2012


[sebaygo1]


Tom Woods is hosting for Peter Schiff.

Today's first guest is Lou Fisher, scholar in residence at the Constitution Project & author of Presidential War Power, on Secretary Panetta's insistence that America's war fighting powers derive from ambiguous international organizations.

Today's second guest is Gary Taubes, author of Good Calories, Bad CaloriesWhy We Get Fat, and Why We Get Fat on whether people are really dropping dead from eating red meat.
